ation of informal settlements.&rdquo;In Nelson Mandela Bay, over 220 metro police officers were now patrolling the streets, especially focused on bringing down drug related crimes.Maimane said that, overall, the party was focused on preparing for the elections in 2019.&ldquo;We are determined that Election 2019 will see the end of the ANC&rsquo;s occupation of the Union Buildings,&rdquo; he said.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.